<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA61">
<l>iṟaimuṟaiyāṉ cēvaṭimēṉ maṇṇaḷanta vannāṇ</l>
<l>maṟaimuṟaiyāl vāṉāṭar kūṭi muṟaimuṟaiyiṉ</l>
<l>ṟātilaku pūtteḷittā lovvātē tāḻvicumpiṉ</l>
<l>mītilakit tāṅkiṭakku mīṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That day the lord in sequence measured the earth on [his] red feet,</l>
<l>if those from the heavenly land had joined in the order of the Vedas</l>
<l>[and] strewn flowers shining with pollen turn after turn, would they not resemble</l>
<l>the very stars that lie shining above, on the hanging sky?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
